.Im MicroEmacs variable|buffer|modeline
.so me.tni
.TH $buffer-mode-line 5
.XI $buffer-mode-line - "Buffer mode line string"
.SH NAME
$buffer-mode-line \- Buffer mode line string
.Me $a
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B $buffer-mode-line
"\fIstring\fR"
.SH DESCRIPTION
Sets  the  buffer  mode  line,  unique  to  this  buffer,  see 
.Ht $mode-line 5
use,  description  and  syntax. If this  variable  is NOT set for a buffer and
\fB$mode-line\fR  is changed, then the buffer's  mode line will also change to
the new value. If this  variable is set, then then  buffer's mode line will be
unaffected by any setting of \fB$mode-line\fR.
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.na
.Ht $mode-line 5 .
.ad
